---
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Statistics for Strava">
  <div class="project-wrapper">
    <section class="project-header">
      <h1>Statistics for Strava</h1>
      <div class="project-meta">
        <span class="date">Fall 2025</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="project-content">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="image-section">
          <img 
            src="/project_photos/statistics-for-strava.png" 
            alt="Statistics for Strava website" 
            class="project-image" 
          />
        </div>
        
        <div class="description-section">
          <h2>Project Overview</h2>
          <p>
            A self-hosted analytics dashboard for analyzing my Strava running activities. The platform provides detailed insights into my performance metrics and activity history. It's publicly available at <a href="https://strava.martinstyve.no/" target="_blank" class="inline-link">strava.martinstyve.no</a>.
          </p>

          <p>
            Playing with activity data using the Strava API has been an ongoing side project, but creating a usable analytics platform from scratch always felt too daunting. When I discovered the open-source project <a href="https://github.com/robiningelbrecht/statistics-for-strava" target="_blank" class="inline-link">statistics-for-strava</a>, I decided to give it a shot.
          </p>

          <p>
            As someone with limited but growing Docker experience, deploying this application was an exciting challenge. I learned how to containerize applications and deploy them on my personal server. I've also done some local development work to understand the project architecture and made several minor customizations to fit my needs.
          </p>

          <div class="tech-stack">
            <h3>Technologies Used</h3>
            <div class="tech-tags">
              <span class="tag">Strava API</span>
              <span class="tag">Docker</span>
              <span class="tag">Analytics</span>
              <span class="tag">Data Visualization</span>
              <span class="tag">Self-hosting</span>
              <span class="tag">Containerization</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .project-wrapper {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .project-header {
    padding: 4rem 1rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .project-header h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #5DD5FF;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -1px;
  }

  .project-meta {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .date {
    color: #888;
  }

  .project-content {
    padding: 3rem 1rem;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .image-section {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .project-image {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-width: 400px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 2px solid rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.2);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .project-image:hover {
    border-color: rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.4);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .description-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    color: #5DD5FF;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .description-section p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #c4c4c4;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .inline-link {
    color: #96F7FF;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(150, 247, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .inline-link:hover {
    color: #5DD5FF;
    border-bottom-color: rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.6);
  }

  .tech-stack {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .tech-stack h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: #96F7FF;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .tech-tags {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.1);
    color: #96F7FF;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    border: 1px solid rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.2);
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .tag:hover {
    background: rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.15);
    border-color: rgba(93, 213, 255, 0.4);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .project-header h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .project-meta {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .project-content {
      padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .description-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .description-section p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }
</style>
